ccn = preprocessing.CheckColumnNames()
input_data = pd.DataFrame({'one': [1, 2], 'two': [3, 4], 'three': [5, 6]})
test_data = pd.DataFrame({'one': [7, 8], 'two': [9, 10], 'three': [11, 12],
    'four': [13, 14]})
expected_data = pd.DataFrame({'one': [7, 8], 'two': [9, 10], 'three': [11, 12]}
    )
input_data = input_data[['one', 'two', 'three']]
expected_data = expected_data[['one', 'two', 'three']]
ccn.fit(input_data)
pd.util.testing.assert_frame_equal(ccn.transform(test_data), expected_data)
